_:N7edad43258964f0f83f6a0dc8f57373c <http://schema.org/description> "Chevening Scholarships are the UK government’s global scholarships programme. Established in 1983, these scholarships support study at UK universities - mostly one-year Masters’ degrees - for students with demonstrable potential to become future leaders, decision-makers and opinion formers." .
